# Data Deletion Request Policy for Little Kingdom

**Effective Date:** March 22, 2026

Little Kingdom ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and provides users and parents with the ability to request deletion of any data associated with the app.

---

## 🗑️ Your Right to Request Data Deletion

You have the right to request that we delete any data associated with your use of Little Kingdom.

This includes:

* Gameplay progress data
* Device-related data
* Any stored app interaction data

---

## 👶 Children’s Data Protection

Because Little Kingdom is designed for children, we take extra care to ensure that:

* We do **not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13**
* Parents or guardians can request deletion of any associated data at any time

---

## 📩 How to Request Data Deletion

To request deletion of your data, please contact us using the information below:

**Email:** deaconjason@awillingvessel.org
**Subject Line:** Data Deletion Request – Little Kingdom

Please include:

* Device type (Android, iOS, Web)
* Approximate date of use
* Description of your request

This helps us locate and delete the correct data.

---

## ⏱️ Processing Time

We will process all data deletion requests within **7–14 business days**.

Once completed:

* Your data will be permanently deleted
* It cannot be recovered

---

## 🔒 Data Retention

We only retain limited non-personal data for:

* Improving app performance
* Debugging and fixing issues

This data is either anonymized or deleted upon request.

---

## 🌍 Third-Party Services

If any third-party services are used (such as hosting or analytics), we will:

* Request deletion of your data from those services
* Ensure they comply with privacy standards

---

## ⚠️ Limitations

In rare cases, we may retain minimal data if required by law or for security purposes.

---

## 🔄 Updates to This Policy

We may update this policy as needed. Updates will be reflected with a new effective date.

---

